verses.roman:
tapana-miśrere āra candraśekharere
prabhu-ājñāya sanātana mililā doṅhāre

synonyms: tapana-miśrere—unto Tapana Miśra; āra—and; candraśekharere—unto Candraśekhara; prabhu-ājñāya—by the order of Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu; sanātana—Sanātana; mililā—met; doṅhāre—both of them.
translation: By the order of Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu, Sanātana Gosvāmī met both Tapana Miśra and Candraśekhara.
